column1: Which provides regular expression matching operations similar to those found in Perl?
Which flag matches the start of a string?
Which flag matches the end of a string?
Which flag matches any single character including newline?
Which flag matches any single character in the set?
Which flag matches any single character not in the set?
Which flag matches the preceding character zero or more times?
Which flag matches the preceding character one or more times?
Which flag matches the preceding character zero or one time?
Which flag matches the preceding character exactly n times?
Which flag matches the preceding character at least n times?
Which flag matches the preceding character at most n times?
